类 InitSmackStaticCode

  com.easemob.chat.InitSmackStaticCode

public class InitSmackStaticCode
extends java.lang.Object

Since dalvik on Android does not allow the loading of META-INF files from the filesystem, the static blocks of some classes have to be inited manually. The full list can be found here: http://fisheye.igniterealtime.org/browse/smack/trunk/build/resources/META-INF/smack-config.xml?hb=true
